# Multi-Hit Cancer Analysis Project

BRCA.maf2dat.matrix.out.test
Num Genes | num patients | random | titles
Gene ID | Patient ID | # Mutations | Gene | File Name for Patient ID again
## Root Files/Folders:
- **README.md**: Overview of multi-hit combination algorithm for cancer mutation analysis
- **src/**: Source code directory containing C programs and Python scripts
- **data/**: Input data directory with mutation matrices and manifest files
- **result/**: Output directory containing identified gene combinations
- **s41598-018-37835-6.pdf**: Research paper reference

## src/ Directory:
- **acc2hit.c**: Main algorithm to identify multi-hit combinations using likelihood ratio
- **validate2hit.c**: Validation program for 3-hit gene combinations 
- **validateNormal2hit.py**: Python script to validate normal samples against combinations
- **compute-multihit-combinations.sh**: Shell script to run full analysis pipeline

## data/maf2dat-moderate/ Directory:
- **BRCA.maf2dat.matrix.out**: Full BRCA mutation matrix (genes x samples)
- **BRCA.maf2dat.matrix.out.training**: Training subset of BRCA data
- **BRCA.maf2dat.matrix.out.test**: Test subset of BRCA data
- **manifest_normal_normal.txt**: Normal tissue sample manifest
- **manifest_normal_normal.txt.geneSampleList**: Gene-sample mutation list for normal tissue

## result/ Directory:
- **ACC2HIT/**: Contains output combinations for different cancer types
- **BRCA/**: BRCA-specific results with identified gene combinations and scores

## Data Format Notes:
- Mutation matrices: Gene ID | Patient ID | # Mutations | Gene | Sample File
- Gene sample lists: Gene | Patient ID (mutated genes per sample)
- Combinations output: 2-gene combo | F-max score | Additional metrics

